<para id="fs-idp63261056">Which color(s) of light does chlorophyll <emphasis effect="italics">a</emphasis> reflect?</para>
<list id="fs-idp26938576" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>red and blue</item>
<item>green</item>
<item>red</item>
<item>blue</item>
</list>
